<h3><img src="/media/13103433/excursion-special-offer-838.jpg" alt="SantaExHero" data-udi="umb://media/28ad0fea2b6a4717823cd875d67fe013" /></h3>
<h2>Santa Experience excursion in Lapland - Save up to £90pp</h2>
<p>Valid on <a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights">7-night Lapland holidays</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Ylläs</a> during November &amp; December 2024/2025 (while stocks last). The Santa Experience is the perfect holiday addition for any family visiting Lapland over the festive period. </p>
<h3>Special offer includes:</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/05d3b1900a534df49444693b1f18fdb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/05d3b1900a534df49444693b1f18fdb0}" title="Santa’s Elves Hideaway">Santa's Elves Hideaway</a> - Make mischief with Santa's elves before your special meeting with Santa himself</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec}" title="Husky Rides">Husky Safari</a> – Weave through the frozen landscape with your team of huskies</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719" href="/{localLink:umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719}" title="Reindeer Rides">Reindeer Safari </a>- Ride in a reindeer sleigh between the snow-covered trees</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/104675d8a38c4beaac3c4b4532d057f0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/104675d8a38c4beaac3c4b4532d057f0}" title="The climate in Lapland">Thermal boots and suit</a> - These cosy thermal overalls and protective snow boots will be included for the duration of your stay</p>
<p><em>*Offer includes full length excursions - see the T&amp;C's at the bottom of this page for full details.</em></p>
<h3>Santa Experience excursion options available per resort:</h3>
<p> </p>
