<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><img src="/media/13049993/santa.jpg" alt="santainsleigh" data-udi="umb://media/ea02722f7d264695a5cc480ca118eb6e" /><br />
<h3>What’s included in the Santa's Elves Hideaway excursion: </h3>
<p>Santa's home is hidden away in a snowy, magic forest - full of atmosphere and fun for the children. Visit one of Santa's workshops and meet his elves, take part in Elf school and various snow games for youngsters - tobogganing and snowballs are always on the agenda. Plus of course, there's the highlight of the day - meeting with Santa Claus himself.</p>
</div>
