<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Save up to 20%</li>
<li>Save £90 in Levi, £90 in Ylläs &amp; £65 in Saariselkä (savings based on adult prices)</li>
<li>Valid on 7-night holidays to Lapland winter November/December 2025 &amp; 2026 subject to availability</li>
<li>Offer not applicable to infants aged 0 - 3 years</li>
<li>Excursion experiences and durations vary between resorts and dependent on weather conditions. Applicable to following excursions in:<br />- Levi - Santa's Elves Hideaway (private meeting with Santa), 8km Husky Safari, 3km Reindeer Safari &amp; Thermal Suits and Boots               <br />- Ylläs - Santa's Hideaway (private meeting with Santa), 9km Husky Safari, 1.5km Reindeer Safari &amp; Thermal Suits and Boots                  <br />- Saariselkä - Visit Santa's Home (group meeting with Santa), 5km Husky Safari &amp; Reindeer Safari (Thermal Suits &amp; Boots are already included for all guests in Saariselkä)              </li>
<li>Excursion days and times will be advised on arrival in resort</li>
<li>Offer is subject to availability and may be withdrawn at any time</li>
<li>Not valid on 3 &amp; 4 night Santa Breaks</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Cancellation:</strong> If you choose to cancel or if you choose not to participate in an excursion for whatever reason, the supplier’s terms and conditions will apply. In the event of cancellation of a qualifying excursion, the cost of the excursion (minus the 20% saving) will be deducted from any refund due.</p>
